short.ar: اكسب النقاط دون لمس المكعبات على المنصة باستخدام مكعب دودو.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Get ready to dodge obstacles from below with a sweet cube! Make your best score in this adventure game.

How To Play
Played with Arrow Keys.

Dodo Cube Arcade Game Features
✓ 2D Graphics
✓ Easy control
✓ Fun Sounds
✓ 2D Character
✓ Infinity Level

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Dodo Cube Arcade Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
